title: Grateful Dead Live at Providence Civic Center on 1986-04-01
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Gimme Some Lovin'-> Little Red Rooster, Stagger Lee, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain-> Big Railroad Blues-> The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Shakedown Street, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> I Need A Miracle-> Black Peter-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Box Of Rain
